name: M.2 128GB SSD Drive
description: Ramsta R600 M.2 SSD delivers all the advantages of flash disk technology with the M.2 Socket 2 Serial ATA I/II/III interface and is fully compliant with the PCI-SIG M.2 Standard. The SSD is designed with SMI controller, which can perfect support TLC NAND Flash by the hardware LDPC ECC engine or support MLC NAND Flash by the hardware BCH ECC engine. Its capacity could provide a wide range up to 256GB. Moreover, it can reach up to 560MB/s read as well as 420MB/s write high performance based on IM 3D TLC flash (measured by CrystalDiskMark v4.0.3). Meanwhile, the power consumption of the R600 SSD is much lower than traditional hard drives.
